widgets_values:
Unfortunately get/set does not work correctly with bypass.
https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-KJNodes/issues/15

The current series is stored in a persistent variable - a text file; and incremented when starting a new series.
Strangely, something to string fails on noneobj when loading from file so have to use pygoss.
Output only needs to be added for vhs, otherwise it's automatic.

Bbox is slightly better than segm for the purpose of cropping.
I don't think I really need sam2.
The image is preprocessed once; subsequent gens must have an identical frame size for the video to be combinable.
Overwrites current_series without creating a new one - for continuing an existing series from its last current_frame.

Once the series is complete, run ffmpeg merge to make a single vid. Can cleanup the temp vids if desired. Should automatically skip the same number of frames as used in the current_frame saver for optimal fluidity.
